```
hello.c
   │
   ▼
Preprocessor
   │
   ▼
Expanded C Code
   │
   ▼
Compiler
   │
   ▼
Assembly Code (.s)
   │
   ▼
Assembler
   │
   ▼
Object File (.o)
   │
   ▼
Linker
   │
   ▼
Executable (a.out)
```

## 5. Useful `cc` Options

| Command               | Meaning                         |
| --------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| `cc hello.c`          | compile and link                |
| `cc -o hello hello.c` | output executable named `hello` |
| `cc -c hello.c`       | compile only (create `.o`)      |
| `cc -Wall hello.c`    | show warnings                   |
| `cc -g hello.c`       | add debugging info              |

